_sText:
A fun fair map for 2 sides which are Terrorist - Nazi Germany & Counter-Terrorist - Soviet Russia. Map has 2 side Trenches and underground passage to fight in close combat and top for scout/awp combat. name of map fy_tundra_v2_fixed because I did mistake in v2 and I didnt want to make it v3. map has its skybox_camera which makes it more realistic and snow falling down. 

Enjoy.
